It isn't about the future; or the past. It's about being in the present. So much of our life is dictated by a future that is far from guaranteed. We are born into a system that constricts. That devalues; that takes your energy, consumes it and gives you back a fraction of what you spent to create it. 

Banks, institutions, VC firms. They are all the same. They take more than they give. Not just in  fiat, but time. You know what the most precious thing in life is. Time. It's the only thing money can't buy you. 

Discombobulate is an Ethos, an idea. Its a refusal to play by the rules of the system. It's a gambler who walks into a rigged casino and realizes they can't win. Instead he steps outside to the curb and lights the money on fire. He knew the money was gone either way. He refused the system and did the only thing they hate. He took their control away and made them watch what they cherished burn.

This is an idea. I'm only one man, maybe less. I need help. I have an idea but I need to find my family out there. 

Are you a Discombobulator? I know you are out there...... Somewhere.
